t)\">Jeff Sonas</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Rainer_Staudte\" title=\"Rainer Staudte\">Rainer Staudte</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ken_Thompson\" title=\"Ken Thompson\">Ken Thompson</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Vossen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Peter Vossen (page does not exist)\">Peter Vossen</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Wallendik&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Thomas Wallendik (page does not exist)\">Thomas Wallendik</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Klaus_Wlotzka&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Klaus Wlotzka (page does not exist)\">Klaus Wlotzka</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hans_Zellner\" title=\"Hans Zellner\">Hans Zellner</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Stefan_Zipproth\" title=\"Stefan Zipproth\">Stefan Zipproth</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Computerschach_und_Spiele&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=286508\">qBASIC Chess program - from 1984 by Dieter Steinwender</a> by <a href=\"/Michael_Byrne\" title=\"Michael Byrne\">Mike Byrne</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 23, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Basic\" title=\"Basic\">Basic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=9988\">Nostalgic Flash Back</a> by Michael L. (blaubaer), <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Hiarcs Forum</a>,  May 11, 2020</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Computerschach_und_Spiele&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computerschach.de/\">Computerschach und Spiele online</a> (German)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computerschach_und_Spiele\">Computerschach und Spiele from Wikipedia</a> (German)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://forum.computerschach.de/\">CSS Forum</a> (German)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computerschach.de/index.php?option=com_wrapper&amp;Itemid=238\">CSS Rating List</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Computerschach_und_Spiele&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computerschach.com/index.php?option=com_akolegal&amp;Itemid=45\">Computerschach und Spiele, Impressum</a> (German)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.steinwender.de/cms/front_content.php?idcat=39\">Steinwender EDV-Beratung GbR</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://scleinzell.schachvereine.de/p_themen/chronik.shtml\">Schachclub Leinzell - Chr